4. Jupyter Notebooks#

4.1. What are Jupyter Notebooks?#

Notebooks are documents combining executable code with narrative text - literate programming

A cell can have different type

Code: Executable code Markdown: Markdown formatted text Raw: Plain text

When executing a “Code” cell, its code is sent to a execution kernel. Its name and its status are displayed here and in the status bar.
